{"word":"Benjamin","slug":"benjamin","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Benjamin</b> <a href=\"#/H1144\">H1144</a> <br/> 1. Son of Jacob by Rachel<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=18'>Gen 35:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=24'>Gen 35:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=19'>Gen 46:19</a> <br/> - Taken into Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42'>Gen 42</a> <br/> - Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=27'>Gen 49:27</a> <br/> - Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=21'>Gen 46:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=41'>Num 26:41</a> <br/> 2. Tribe of<br/> - Census of:<br/> b Sinai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=37'>Num 1:37</a><br/> b the plain of Moab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=41'>Num 26:41</a><br/> - Clans of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=40'>Num 26:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=12'>1Ch 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8'>1Ch 8</a> <br/> - Position of, in camp and march<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=18'>Num 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=22'>Num 2:22</a> <br/> - Moses' benediction upon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=12'>Deu 32:12</a> <br/> - Allotment in the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=28'>Jos 18:28</a> <br/> - Reallotment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=48&verse=23'>Eze 48:23</a> <br/> - Did not exterminate the Jebusites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=21'>Jdg 1:21</a> <br/> - Join Deborah in the war against Sisera<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=5&verse=14'>Jdg 5:14</a> <br/> - Territory of, invaded by the Ammonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=10&verse=9'>Jdg 10:9</a> <br/> - Did not avenge the crime of the Gibeonites against the Levite's concubine, the war that followed<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - Saul, the first king of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=1'>1Sa 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=17'>1Sa 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=21'>1Sa 10:21</a> <br/> - Its rank in the time of Samuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=21'>1Sa 9:21</a> <br/> - Jerusalem within the territory of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=1'>Jer 6:1</a> <br/> - A company of, joins David at Ziklag<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=2'>1Ch 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=16'>1Ch 12:16</a> <br/> - Not enrolled by Joab when he took a census of the military forces of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=21&verse=6'>1Ch 21:6</a> <br/> - Loyal to Ish-Bosheth, the son of Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=9'>2Sa 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=15'>2Sa 2:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=31'>2Sa 2:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=29'>1Ch 12:29</a> <br/> - Subsequently joins David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=19'>2Sa 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=17'>2Sa 